name: James Prado
description: My name is JamesPrado…..i’m from Austin city in Texas..love swimming,dancing,camping,going out with my right woman i’m here for a serious relationship that can lead to marriage and a woman that is trustworthy,honest,open-minded,caring.loving and God fearing woman..i’m not here for games……I am looking for someone that enjoys the simple things in life, just as I do. i would like to meet someone special that I can grow old with, and that we can always look into each other’s eyes and know that the love between us is just as wonderful and exciting as the day we met
